de.susebox.jtopas
Class TokenizerPropertyEvent

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--de.susebox.jtopas.TokenizerPropertyEvent
public class TokenizerPropertyEvent
extends java.lang.Object

The class TokenizerPropertyEvent describes changes in TokenizerProperties objects. Instances of this class are produced by TokenizerProperties and passed to TokenizerPropertyListener objects that are registered with the issuing TokenizerProperties instance.

Author:
Heiko Blau
See Also:
TokenizerProperties, TokenizerPropertyListener
